title: Apple Blossoms Apple crumble and apple berry flavors | 4 Servings
description: What could be better than a tender, flaky pastry filled with fall fruit flavors? Two blossoms are filled with apples and cinnamon, topped with a buttery cinnamon-oat crumble, and two are filled with a cozy medley of apples, blackberries, raspberries, and wild blueberries! They’re irresistibly sweet, satisfying, and all-around delicious! When you’re ready to dig in, simply warm them up. You can even enjoy them chilled or at room temperature—we’re big fans of the “less-is-more” philosophy. (Psst—we highly recommend serving with a scoop of vanilla ice cream.)

