2 unit Apple Berry Blossoms
2 unit Crumble Crunch Apple Blossom

RECOMMENDED: Keep frozen until ready to eat; best if used within 7 days. Remove plastic wrap from trays; microwave until warmed through, 50-60 seconds. (Do not overheat.)

OVEN ALTERNATIVE: Keep frozen or refrigerated until ready to eat; best if used within 7 days. If frozen, thaw in the refrigerator (at 40 degrees) overnight or at room temperature for 2-3 hours before baking. Adjust rack to middle position and preheat oven to 350 degrees. Remove plastic wrap from trays; place on a baking sheet and bake until warmed through, 15-20 minutes. (Note: Oven times may vary.)